title: 164: Scouting Combine recap
itunes:title: 164: Scouting Combine recap
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks recap the 2017 Scouting Combine. Will Christian McCaffrey be drafted ahead of Dalvin Cook? Could John Ross be the first wide receiver off the board? DJ and Bucky break it down and analyze the QB class and the freak athletes on defense.
